    [media] bttv: move fini_bttv_i2c() from bttv-input.c to bttv-i2c.c
    
    Like init_bttv_i2c(), fini_bttv_i2c() belongs to bttv-i2c.c.
    
    Signed-off-by: Frank Sch√§fer <fschaefer.oss@googlemail.com>
